What is "DC-chain financing"?
		\nDC-chain financial management is based on the development of digital assets financial products, product risk is low, stable income, with different products to meet the needs of customers, users can freely choose investment according to their own digital assets;
		\nHow to calculate the revenue?
		\nfor each financial product, an annualized rate of return will be pre evaluated for reference only. The income is affected by the amount of investment and the number of promoters as well as the purchase management of related personnel. If the users recommended by the old users purchase the financial products or exchange them for participating in the financial management products, the old users can increase the financial management income from the financial management situation of the new users recommended by them; the more recommended, the more associated new users More, will greatly increase financial income;
		\nHow to distribute the income?
		\nThe income will be distributed every 24 hours from the next day when the financial products are purchased; if the income is distributed according to the agreement, all the financial management income will be distributed, that is, the cooperation cycle of financial products will end;
		\n risk tips: digital assets are innovative investment products, and their prices fluctuate greatly. Please judge your investment ability rationally and make investment decisions carefully.

